Class MockRouteTableController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tlswe.awsmock.ec2.control.MockRouteTableController

  • public final class MockRouteTableController
extends java.lang.Object
    Factory class providing static methods for managing life cycle of mock RouteTable. The current implementations can:
    • create
    • delete
    • describe
    mock RouteTable.
